daptive procedure obtained for one-way classified\nhypotheses is alternative to and often more powerful than those proposed in Hu\net al. (2010).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 Dec 2018 22:44:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 9 Mar 2019 03:33:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-12"}
