ream neutral mode. Here, we also show that even the\nparticle-like quasiparticles are accompanied by upstream neutral modes,\ntherefore suppressing interference in the FQHE regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2018 11:46:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
