 of\nshort packets, for both downlink (DL) and uplink (UL). Finally, we present bit\nerror rate (BER) results, obtained through simulations of a dual-hop DF IEEE\n802.11ah relay system for the considered MCs. All presented results confirm\nthat IEEE 802.11ah systems, through deployment of relay stations, become an\ninteresting solution for M2M and IoT based applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2018 12:38:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-18"}
