uctures\nare revealed by proper orthogonal decomposition of the velocity field. This\nwork presents a new class of problems that requires further theoretical and\nexperimental investigation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2018 15:36:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-18"}
